about: I'm a young professional from Sweden, living in Amsterdam. I came to Amsterdam to study hospitality management and business, but after finishing my degree I realized it is not my dream to work in the hospitality industry but have found myself working with sales in the tech industry. I have a great passion for food, drinks and good service. I have been living in the city centre of Amsterdam for almost 6 years. I love this city and have many good tips for a great time. I am currently living with my boyfriend and am therefore a host on Airbnb.
school: Viktor Rydberg Gymnasium, Stockholm University, Kulturama, Hotelschool The Hague
